Package: hihai
Title: Healthcare-Associated Infections Data Explorer with Shiny
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Arisara", "Therdthianwong", email = "athe0025@student.monash.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Interactive tools for exploring Healthcare-Associated Infections (HAIs) in Germany 
  using data from 2011 ECDC Point Prevalence Survey. The package includes reproducible datasets 
  and Shiny application for visualising that enables comparison of burden and severity among five 
  HAI types in Germany and international comparison with EU/EEA.
